'''{{Path|/usr/portage/profiles}}''' is [[Article description::a directory that contains global [[Profile (Portage)|profiles]] that are controlled by developers of the main ebuild repository (gentoo.git)]]. One of them needs to be [[Handbook:AMD64/Installation/Base#Choosing_the_right_profile|selected as the system profile]]. To override these settings, use the files in the {{Path|[[:/etc/portage|/etc/portage/profile/]]}} directory.

